This paper deals with hyperparameter optimization for machine learning algorithms, which is a common problem in the field of machine learning. The paper also introduces a new algorithm called Hyperband, which is specifically designed for this problem. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
